---
// Capabilities - 4 modules with staggered grid
---

<section id="capabilities" class="border-b border-[var(--color-border)]">
  <div class="max-w-[1400px] mx-auto">
    <!-- Section header -->
    <div class="border-b border-[var(--color-border)] px-4 md:px-8 py-4">
      <div class="flex items-center justify-between">
        <h2 class="macro-type text-lg md:text-xl">
          <span class="text-[var(--color-fg-secondary)]">[ </span>Capabilities<span class="text-[var(--color-fg-secondary)]"> ]</span>
        </h2>
        <span class="micro-type text-[10px]">MODULE INDEX</span>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Capabilities grid - 2x2 with cross borders -->
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2">
      <!-- Capability 1 -->
      <div class="p-6 md:p-10 border-b md:border-r border-[var(--color-border)]">
        <div class="flex items-start justify-between mb-6">
          <span class="macro-type text-5xl md:text-6xl text-[var(--color-accent)]">01</span>
          <span class="micro-type text-[10px] text-[var(--color-terminal-green)]">● ACTIVE</span>
        </div>
        <h3 class="macro-type text-xl md:text-2xl mb-4">Predictive Analytics</h3>
        <p class="data-readout leading-relaxed mb-6">
          Advanced machine learning models trained on 42.8B tokens of market data, 
          social sentiment, and on-chain metrics. Real-time pattern recognition 
          with sub-200ms inference latency.
        </p>
        <div class="data-readout text-[var(--color-fg-primary)]">
          F1 SCORE: 0.967 // AUC-ROC: 0.984
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Capability 2 -->
      <div class="p-6 md:p-10 border-b border-[var(--color-border)]">
        <div class="flex items-start justify-between mb-6">
          <span class="macro-type text-5xl md:text-6xl text-[var(--color-accent)]">02</span>
          <span class="micro-type text-[10px] text-[var(--color-terminal-green)]">● ACTIVE</span>
        </div>
        <h3 class="macro-type text-xl md:text-2xl mb-4">Risk Assessment</h3>
        <p class="data-readout leading-relaxed mb-6">
          Multi-factor risk scoring engine analyzing portfolio exposure, 
          correlation matrices, and volatility regimes. Automated hedging 
          recommendations with confidence intervals.
        </p>
        <div class="data-readout text-[var(--color-fg-primary)]">
          SHARPE: 2.34 // SORTINO: 3.12
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Capability 3 -->
      <div class="p-6 md:p-10 md:border-r border-[var(--color-border)]">
        <div class="flex items-start justify-between mb-6">
          <span class="macro-type text-5xl md:text-6xl text-[var(--color-accent)]">03</span>
          <span class="micro-type text-[10px] text-[var(--color-terminal-green)]">● ACTIVE</span>
        </div>
        <h3 class="macro-type text-xl md:text-2xl mb-4">Sentiment Analysis</h3>
        <p class="data-readout leading-relaxed mb-6">
          Natural language processing across 50+ data sources including 
          social media, news feeds, and developer activity. Sentiment 
          scoring with temporal decay functions.
        </p>
        <div class="data-readout text-[var(--color-fg-primary)]">
          SOURCES: 53 // CONFIDENCE: 0.91
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Capability 4 -->
      <div class="p-6 md:p-10">
        <div class="flex items-start justify-between mb-6">
          <span class="macro-type text-5xl md:text-6xl text-[var(--color-accent)]">04</span>
          <span class="micro-type text-[10px] text-[var(--color-terminal-green)]">● ACTIVE</span>
        </div>
        <h3 class="macro-type text-xl md:text-2xl mb-4">Portfolio Optimization</h3>
        <p class="data-readout leading-relaxed mb-6">
          Mean-variance optimization with constraints. Dynamic rebalancing 
          based on regime detection. Tax-loss harvesting integration 
          with real-time execution.
        </p>
        <div class="data-readout text-[var(--color-fg-primary)]">
          ALPHA: +3.2% // DRAWDOWN: -4.1%
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
